</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_433" id="216r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_433_r1l1">Franckfürt </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_433_r1l2"><expan>Lıeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> freunde / Als Jr von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vvegen gemüwet geweſen ſeit </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_433_r1l3">in <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ſachen / als gen <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan> edeln <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> den von Hanaw / des vvir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_433_r1l4"><expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> Erſamen <expan>freuntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> ʒemal <expan>fleiſſıgl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> <expan>danck<ex>en</ex></expan> / Alſo <expan>ſchıcke<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_433_r1l5">cʒu <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>gütlıche<ex>n</ex></expan> tag beẏ ew ʒeſuchen vvılhelm Mendel <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>lıeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_433_r1l6"><expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd Ratgeſellen / vnd <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr ew Jn in <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ſachen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_433_r1l7">günſtiglich beuolhen laſſen vnd Jm beẏgeſtendig furderlich </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_433_r1l8">geraten vnd beholffen ſein wollet Als etc vnd das in <expan>ſolch<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſup<ex>ra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_433" id="216r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Franckfürt </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> freunde, als ir von
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wegen gemüwet gewesen seit in
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> sachen als gen
                            <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan> edeln <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> den von
                        Hanaw, des wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> ersamen
                                <expan>freuntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> zemal
                                <expan>fleissigl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>danck<ex>en</ex></expan>, also <expan>schicke<ex>n</ex></expan> wir
                        czu <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>gütliche<ex>n</ex></expan> tag bey ew ze suchen Wilhelm Mendel,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> und ratgesellen, und
                            <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir ew in in
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> sachen günstiglich bevolhen lassen und im
                        beygestendig, furderlich, geraten und beholffen sein wollet. Als etc. Und
                        das in <expan>solch<ex>en</ex></expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                                <expan>sup<ex>ra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
